data.description: Eager to sell! Gorgeous home in a desirable neighborhood! Shaded corner lot with a side entry garage. Enjoy the open concept of the large living room, kitchen and dining room that are great for entertaining! Oversized garage with space for a workbench. Updated City Park within walking distance.  This is a must see!
